                    .helper__stepper-navs
                        button.upper-link previous            
                        button.upper-link next
                .helper__content
                    .helper__step.tf-content
                        img(src="img/demo/dmimg.jpg", alt="")

                        p In the work of the Telegram messenger, there was a global failure. This is evidenced by the statistics of the site Downdetector.
                        p Messenger works with interruptions in Russia, Belarus, Ukraine, as well as in the EU countries - Germany, France, Italy, Spain, the Netherlands, Austria, Sweden and other countries.
                        p "If you read this, you are resistance" Roskomnadzor is fighting with Telegram. The whole Internet suffers The failures are also reported by residents of South Africa, Iran, Israel and Kazakhstan.
                        p Telegram unsuccessfully trying to block in Russia, starting in mid-April. According to the decision of the Tagansky District Court of Moscow, access to the messenger should be limited, since the Telegram management refused to provide the FSB with encryption keys that would allow the siloviki to read the correspondence of users.

